instruction: Go past the kitchen island and turn left. Go through the kitchen and stop when the antique scale is on the left.Walk to the far end of the kitchen and wait by the dining table.

Walk past the foot of the stairs leading upwards and then turn left, going down four steps.Walk forward and go down the stairs. Walk past the kitchen on your right and stop in the living room next to the love seat.

Walk straight and then turn right to exit the room. Turn left and go down the hallway. Turn left when you get to large glass doors on the right and wait near the clear vase with the white flowers.Turn right, and walk a bit, and turn left. Walk towards the black chairs, and turn right. Stop in front of the refrigerator.

Turn around and walk across the room and exit. Once out, walk forward and turn right when you reach the bookcase to your left. Turn left and walk through the kitchen storage area and through the kitchen and stop when you reach the end of the counter.Go past the kitchen island and turn left. Go through the kitchen and stop when the antique scale is on the left.

Move ahead in between bar and table to the chair.Walk from the table with the signed helmet and go to the television. At the television turn around and go down the stairs and wait at the bottom of the stairs.

Exit the bedroom and take the first right. Stop just past the eye exam chart on the wall.Walk down the hallway towards the windows. Pass the kitchen and keep going. Take a right and stop next to the rug in front of the couch.

Go straight into the kitchen, turn left and go passed the bar. Go to the end of the hallway and stop in front of the sink and shelves.Walk into the kitchen and go to the left once you pass the counters. Go straight into the small room with the sink. Stop next to the door.
Walk down the stairs and make a sharp turn left. Walk down the steps and stop on the bottom step.Turn and go down the hallway, past the stairs. Enter the living room on the right.

Walk passed the dining table and continue towards the kitchen. Walk through the kitchen passed the counters and stove and stop near the sink.Exit the room and walk straight through the next open door. Continue straight through the kitchen until you reach the wooden table. Wait here.
Go down the stairs and at the landing go down the next set. Stop at the bottom on the wood floor and wait there.Turn right at stairs and go down them. Stop between the bathroom and laundry rooms.

Turn around and walk towards the bookshelf. Once you reach the bookshelf turn right and walk down the hallway to the end and turn right. Stop at when you reach the narrow table.Keeping the hanging wall mirror on your right, proceed onward up the hall until you reach another hallway on your left, go down that left hallway. You will know you are on the correct path if you see a framed photo of letters on the right wall. Continue moving forward until you pass the room on the left with the sink. Pivot to your right and travel in a forward direction down across the tile and then take a step onto the carpet in front of you. Stand on that carpet and wait for further instructions.

Walk up stairs, turn left and stop in bedroom.Walk out of the bedroom and take the first left into another bedroom. In the next bedroom take the second left into the bathroom. Stop in the doorway to the bathroom.

Exit the room using the door on the right. Turn left and go down the stairs on your left. Stop at the end.Turn around and go to the bottom of the stairs. At the bottom turn around and walk to the left side of the stairs towards the dining table. Continue past the dining table and stop in the doorway on the other side.

Exit the bedroom and walk down the stairs to the bottom. Wait on the last step.Walk up the stairwell to the upper floor of the home. Walk into the open door nearest to the top of the stairs, which has two chairs in a corner of the room and a bed.

Walk through the open double doorway next to the long wooden table. Continue straight back inside through the next doorway. Once inside, in the room with the round table and four chairs, go stand in the first doorway on the right.Walk through dining room. Walk through tv room. Walk through open french doors. Wait under wooden archway.
Exit the living room. Go to the bottom of the staircase. Go to the toilet at the end of the hall.Walk past the foot of the stairs leading upwards and then turn left, going down four steps.
Walk straight into the hallway. Turn right and go into the room. Wait near the door on the left.Exit the closet and go to the right. Enter the door and go to the left and go to the end and stop.
Walk from the table with the signed helmet and go to the television. At the television turn around and go down the stairs and wait at the bottom of the stairs.Go up the stairs then stop.

Go up stairs and turn left to stairs. Stop between stairs and large double doors.Walk up stairs. At top of stairs turn right. Walk straight to bedroom. Turn left and walk to bed lamp.Turn left and enter closet. Stop at rug.

Exit the room, turn right and go down the stairs, turn right and right again to the keep going down stairs, when you have reached the bottom stop.Go toward the staircase. Go up the stairs. At the top of the stairs, go through the door that leads to the outside. Turn into the first door on the right. Enter the toilet. Stop there.

Face the walkway with a kitchen counter with bar stools on the right and large windows on the other side and walk past them towards a large dining table Turn to the sitting area and stop.Walk into the kitchen, walk past the stove, wait near the telephone.

Exit the bedroom. Turn left continue down the hallway until you get to the stairs. Wait there.Turn to your left and enter the sitting room. Once in, turn right and walk past the dining room table. Stop in the doorway on the other side, looking into the kitchen.
Ascend stairs, then walk toward the kitchen area, and wait.Enter the kitchen and walk past the refrigerator, then turn right. Proceed through the entryway and wait by the freezers.

Walk into the kitchen, walk past the stove, wait near the telephone.Walk from telephone down hall and turn left down hall just before vase. Walk through archway into bedroom. Stop between bed and chair.

Walk toward the left, down the stairs and through the doorway. Then turn right, walk into the room on the right and wait by the massage table.Walk through doorway towards the tub, turn left and walk towards the bar, right before the bar turn left, walk up the stairs and walk through the first door on the right, stop right before the table.

Walk out of the bedroom and turn right. Walk into the bedroom and turn right. Stop just inside the closet.Exit the closet and go the bedroom. Turn left and exit the bedroom. Walk straight to the top of the stairs and turn right. Walk straight forward and enter the bedroom in from of you. Wait just inside the doorway.

Walk down the flight of stairs then make a right and wait on the steps in front of the bathroom.Walk up the stairwell to the upper floor of the home. Walk into the open door nearest to the top of the stairs, which has two chairs in a corner of the room and a bed.
Walk into and through the kitchen. Stop next to the long wooden dining table.Walk straight into the hallway. Turn right and go into the room. Wait near the door on the left.
Follow the kitchen island around to the left. Enter the dining room through the door left of the oven. Pass the dining table and wait there.Go up the stairs. Stop at the top of the stairs.

Walk forward into the house and past the living room. Keep going forward into the dining room. Stop at the first corner to the dining table closest to the patio door.Walk between the the kitchen counter and the couch and down the hall. Stop near the mirror that is hanging on the left side of the hallway.
Walk past the furniture and to the left of the stairs. Stop by the post at the top of the stairs.Walk straight then talk a right at the window and wait by the pool table.

Walk away from the fireplace, past the table. Go through the door and up the stairs. Go past the first landing. Stop on the second stair up from the landing.Walk all the way up both the stairs to reach the top of the stairs. Turn right towards the very first corner and stop right there.

Go down the hallway past the mirror. Turn left at the picture with the letters. Step through the doorway into the kitchen.Walk into the kitchen and go to the left once you pass the counters. Go straight into the small room with the sink. Stop next to the door.
Go up the small staircase. Turn right, Go to the second stair going down and stop.Turn left, and walk down the stairs. Keep walking forward towards the dining table, and stop there.

Step down from the stars and turn hard left around the corner. Walk down Four steps and wait at the entrance to the kitchen.Turn left and go up the stairs. Turn right to go up more stairs. Keep going up until you are on the third stair.
Go straight into the kitchen, turn left and go passed the bar. Go to the end of the hallway and stop in front of the sink and shelves.Go to the far end of the kitchen and wait in the sitting area.

Go straight and turn right in front of the towards the 3 wicker decorations. Go straight down the hallway, enter the doorway, and wait.walk towards top of the stairs, walk past stairs and turn right, walk through doorway turn right and stop once you walk through two glass doors.
Turn left then go out to the balcony using the door on the right.Go straight ahead through the double doors, then walk past the bed.Take a right toward the hallway, and stop in the entrance.

Walk down stairs, turn right at the bottom and go down steps. Wait at bottom of steps.Step down from the stars and turn hard left around the corner. Walk down Four steps and wait at the entrance to the kitchen.

go trough the doorway and take a hard left then walk straight towards the archway and then keep going until you are under the archway and then stop.Go through the doorway to the bedroom and walk past the bed to the door on the right. Enter the bathroom and stop by the first sink.

Walk up the first flight of black stairs. Wait by door at the bottom of second flight of steps.Walk into the house and go up the stairs. Once you are up the first set of stairs enter the dining room through the door that is second on the left. Stop one you are on the rug near the cabinet near the doorway.

Go to your right passed the couch and the coffee table. Go to the pool table and then stop next to the window.walk across living room behind couch, turn left at couch, Walk directly across the living room, stop at stairs.

Walk into the living room and keep walking straight past the living room. Then walk into the entrance under the balcony. Wait in the entrance to the other room.Go up all the stairs and stop on the rug at the top.

Walk forward, and go up the stairs. Go up the next set of stairs passing the hieroglyphs. Stop at the top of this set of stairs.Walk up the stairs and wait on the second step of the second set of stairs.

Head all the way up the first set of stairs. Go forward and turn right into the next set of stairs with brown carpet. Go up 3 steps. Wait there.Go down the stairs and turn slightly right to get to the wooden table with the eight black chairs. Wait there.

Enter the bedroom. Turn left and exit the bedroom through the door. Wait by stairs.Go down the stairs and at the bottom, step sideways to the left and then go down the hallway with the wooden door at the end. Enter the room to the right of the wooden door and stop once you have entered.

Walk out the clear glass door. Make a right and go all the way down the stairs. Stop in front of the first palm tree.Go straight until you pass all the couches and chairs. Stop by the large picture of the bridge.

Head all the way up the first set of stairs. Go forward and turn right into the next set of stairs with brown carpet. Go up 3 steps. Wait there.Turn left after the stairs and go straight down the hallway. When you get to the kitchen wait near the table and black chairs.
Exit the room, and walk up the stairs. Wait by the map on the wall near the top.Go up the stairs. Wait beside the support pillar for the stairs.

Walk past the large dining table with the chandelier overhead. The table should be on your right as you walk past it. Follow the red carpet to exit that room by the first doorway you come to after passing the table. There are some red chairs just to the right of the doorway you will go through. Walk down the hall and stop in the first doorway on your right.Go through the doorway with the desk on the right, make a left, go straight passed the stairs on the right and go to the doorway and wait.
Exit the bathroom and turn right to walk out of the bedroom. Walk to the top of the stairs and stop on the third step down.enter bedroom, proceed into bathroom.

walk away from sink, turn left, walk towards foot of bed, exit through doorway on left, turn right and step down two stairs and stop.With the stairs leading downwards to your immediate right, move forward into the bedroom. Upon entering the bedroom, go left and enter the dressing area towards your left near the head of the bed. Counting counter-wise with the door to the immediate left of the opening to the bedroom being number one, go to the third door which will allow you access to the toilet.

walk through the doorway directly opposite and slightly to the left of the fireplace, turn left in the hallway and walk down the staircase on the left stop in the doorway to the outside.Go forward and make a left to the bottom of the stairs. Head up the steps and go left to head up the second set of steps. Wait near the stair landing.

Walk through the open door to the right of the boxes on the floor. Walk past the bathroom on the left. Walk down the stairs to the left. Wait on the area rug on the stair landing.Walk down the stairs and make a sharp turn right. Walk down the stairs and stop at the bottom of the stairs.

Go through living room, through the door on the to the right, through the den, through the dining to, to the outdoor foyer. Stop before going outside.Go through the double doors and walk straight. Bear to the right and exit through the open sliding glass doors. Turn to the right and stand and wait by the corner of the pool table.
Exit the bathroom, turn right, walk down the hallway, turn left, wait at the front door to the house.Walk up the stairs, turn left, make another left, stop near the bedroom doorway.

Walk along the grass until you reach the sidewalk near the patio stairs. Walk up the stairs and across the patio. Walk through the sliding glass doors. Walk straight ahead and turn right into the kitchen.Turn around, go past the fridge, and then turn right and go up the steps. Just when you get to the top of the steps, stop. Wait there.
Go straight into the hall. Turn right and walk straight until you go into another room. Wait there.Walk into the dining room and go back to the door across the room. Go through the door and wait.

walk straight along edge of pool, turn slight left and continue towards counter. Turn left and go up stairs. Stop at the double open doors.Climb the three steps next to you and continue forward, climbing three more steps. Stay straight and pass through the door opening directly ahead of you, then stop next to the massage table.

Turn around where you stand and walk around to chair to your left and continue forward to the end of the wood counter to your right. Turn slightly to your right and walk past the pillar that is between the lamp and the stairs going down. Stop between the pillar and the stairs.Take a left around the lamp, go straight along the dresser drawers and go straight and stop in front of the glass doors.

Go through living room, through the door on the to the right, through the den, through the dining to, to the outdoor foyer. Stop before going outside.Locate the large painting above the teapot. Go through the door to the right of it. Pass the white couch and go through the door to the right of the fireplace. Travel to the brown couch with the pillow.

Walk through the doorway, take a left through the 2nd doorway, stop right before the plant on the right side.Go down the hall past some plants towards a doorway to the hot tub and some lounge chairs. Stop in front of the large tub.

Leave the room between the two columns past the antelope. Turn Left and exit into the hallway. Turn left again and go down the stairs. Stop at the door down stairs just before the exit to the building and wait there.Walk down the stairs. Turn right after the display case on the right. Walk into the kitchen and take a right. Wait in the entry way of the next room.
Take a left around the lamp, go straight along the dresser drawers and go straight and stop in front of the glass doors.turn right and go up the stairs and stand at the top.

Turn 90 degrees to the right. Walk straight through the doorway, stop. Turn 90 degrees to the left. Walk straight. Go through the doorway. Keeping straight, stay to the right. Go up the five steps. Continue going straight. Turn into the first doorway on the left, stop.Go to the bottom of the staircase. Go down to the bottom of the staircase. Turn immediately right and go to the bottom of the staircase and stop.
Go down the hallway past the mirror. Turn left at the picture with the letters. Step through the doorway into the kitchen.Walk to the far end of the kitchen and wait by the dining table.

Exit the room and walk into the room with the pool in it. Turn right and walk down the room and through the beaded doorway. After passing through the beads, turn left and stop just in front of the door to the wooden sauna room.Exit the sauna then go out the beaded curtain on the right. Turn left on the first door and wait by the table.

Exit the sitting room and make a right. Walk past the urns on the floor. Make a hard right just after the stairs. Walk past the four photos of flowers on the right. Walk through the open door. Wait on the area rug.Exit the room and then go down the hallway until you get a frame on the wall to your right with a bear and balloons that says "welcome" and wait there.
Turn around, go past the fridge, and then turn right and go up the steps. Just when you get to the top of the steps, stop. Wait there.You should walk up the two flights of stairs and wait at the top.

Walk up the first flight of black stairs. Wait by door at the bottom of second flight of steps.Go down the stairs and turn right. Keep going down the stairs and stop in the doorway of the living room.
Go down the staircase and at the bottom stop.Walk up stairs into sitting room, stop next to coffee table.

walk across bedroom to open door, enter sitting room and continue straight down hall, turn left into bathroom. Stop at sink.Exit the bedroom, and walk forward. Turn left at the corner, and make another left inside the room that has the big black alphabet frame on the wall in the outside. Enter the room and stop there.

Go through the hallway, make a right near the top of the stairs, take a few steps downstairs and then wait.Walk down the flight of stairs then make a right and wait on the steps in front of the bathroom.
Turn around and then turn right to walk all the way down the stairs. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.Go up the stairs. Wait beside the support pillar for the stairs.

Head past the bar along the side of the pool. Turn right and stop inside of the sauna.Exit the room and walk into the room with the pool in it. Turn right and walk down the room and through the beaded doorway. After passing through the beads, turn left and stop just in front of the door to the wooden sauna room.
Walk up the stairs, turn left and walk into the middle bedroom. Wait by the entry way.Go down the stairs and at the landing go down the next set. Stop at the bottom on the wood floor and wait there.

Take a left around the lamp, go straight along the dresser drawers and go straight and stop in front of the glass doors.Leave the dining room, walk through the living room, and wait by the pool table.

With the foot of the bed behind you, exit the bedroom through the door on the left and walk to the top of the stairs. Go through the open door at the top of the stairs and enter the bedroom. Stop after entering this bedroom.Walk down stairs, turn right at the bottom and go down steps. Wait at bottom of steps.
Walk out of the bedroom and turn right. Walk into the bedroom and turn right. Stop just inside the closet.Exit the bathroom, turn left and exit the bedroom. Wait in the hall by the stair case.

Go to the hallway, take a right, and at the intersection take a left, stopping at the bar.Enter the kitchen and walk past the refrigerator, then turn right. Proceed through the entryway and wait by the freezers.

Walk past the center column on the left. Make a right through the open french doors on the right. Walk past the bed on the right. Walk across the area rug. Wait at the open door to the right of the console table.Turn left then go out to the balcony using the door on the right.

Turn around and go up the stairs. Stop at the top of the stairs.Walk forward to the sitting area to the right of the stairs. Walk to the wall of windows and take a right into the recreation room and stop before you reach the pool table.

Walk and turn left around the counter and walk straight towards the living room. Stop next to the couch entrance.Follow the kitchen island around to the left. Enter the dining room through the door left of the oven. Pass the dining table and wait there.

Walk toward the left, down the stairs and through the doorway. Then turn right, walk into the room on the right and wait by the massage table.Go through the doorway and to the left follow straight before the bar and go to the lefft, until you go up the stairway, and take the first right stop at the the massage room.

Walk up the stairs all the way to the top. Walk through the second doorway on your left, and stop immediatly once you walked through.Go down the stairs and at the landing go down the next set. Stop at the bottom on the wood floor and wait there.

Make a left at the end of the bed. Walk to the banister. Walk to the bottom of the stairs to the left of this point. Make a right and move to the panoramic checker doors.Walk up the stairs and take a right. Take another right and walk along the balcony. Stop on the rug in front of the cabinet.

Go to the bed. Go to the shelf. Go to the flower alcove. Go to the stairs. Go down two stairs.Turn to the left and go up the stairs. Go into the bedroom and turn left, go beside the bed, turn left and go through a hallway. Then you'll see a master bathroom. Go just inside the doorway and wait right there.

Walk through the open door to the right of the boxes on the floor. Walk past the bathroom on the left. Walk down the stairs to the left. Wait on the area rug on the stair landing.Walk down the stairs. When you reach the landing, turn right and continue to walk down the stairs. Walk through the doorway on your left and stop.

Walk to the right of the stairs and down the steps. Stop on the bottom step.Turn slightly right and walk towards the glass doorway past the sofas. Exit outside and wait down the steps just before the grass.

Face the walkway with a kitchen counter with bar stools on the right and large windows on the other side and walk past them towards a large dining table Turn to the sitting area and stop.Walk past the kitchen and go behind the couch and take a right into the fitness room. Stop next to the treadmill.

Walk out the shower and through the first doorway on the left. Walk through the doorway directly to the left of dresser, walk through the room and through the first doorway that leads to the stairs. Stop right before the staircase that leads downstairs.Turn to the left and go up the stairs. Go into the bedroom and turn left, go beside the bed, turn left and go through a hallway. Then you'll see a master bathroom. Go just inside the doorway and wait right there.

Face the hanging light to the right of the counter with a sink. Travel straight through the archway that does not lead to the stairs. Keep going until you are in the doorway of the room at the end of the hallway.Walk out of the room and down the hallway. Walk past the kitchen and stop outside of the door to the dining room.

Walk down the stairs and make a sharp turn right. Walk down the stairs and stop at the bottom of the stairs.Walk down the stairs and make a sharp turn right. Walk down the stairs and turn left. Walk forward into the laundry room and stop.
Walk through the bedroom and out into the hall way. Turn left and walk up to the stairs. Walk up to the first step and stop.You should walk up the two flights of stairs and wait at the top.

turn around and walk down the hall. Then go halfway up the stairs and stand next to the second glass rose picture.Walk down stairs. Once you reach the bottom, turn hard left. Enter the room straight ahead. Wait here.

Go up the stairs. Stop at the top of the stairs.Leave the bedroom and walk down the hallway. Go down the stairs and into the living room on the right of the stairwell. In the living room take a right and stand next to the first chair in the dining room.

Go to the bed. Go to the shelf. Go to the flower alcove. Go to the stairs. Go down two stairs.Go down the stairs, take a left and go down the hallway towards the kitchen and living area. Take a left and stop by the couch.
Go straight into the hallway.Enter the open door opposite the stairs to go down. Make a right just before the round bedside table. Walk through the closet. Wait at the toilet.

Turn right and exit the bathroom. Walk down the hallway once you pass the wine cellar, keep to the right to enter the next hallway. Go to the end of that hallway and turn to stop on the bottom step of the stairs.Go down the stairs and take a right. Go down the hall that runs along the stairs. Take the second right past the stairs. Enter the bedroom and stop in the doorway.

Exit the closet into the bedroom. Exit the bedroom through the door on your left and enter into the landing area. Move towards the stairway to the left and stop there.go down stairs, go down hall on left, enter room stop by coffee table.
Go to the far end of the kitchen and wait in the sitting area.Go straight into the kitchen, turn left and go passed the bar. Go to the end of the hallway and stop in front of the sink and shelves.
go straight to the door then turn right.Turn left into the wine cellar. Walk to the end of the room. Wait in front of the table with the barrels underneath it.

Walk straight through the kitchen. Turn slightly right to continue walking straight down the hallway. Turn right and wait near the entrance of the second room on the left.Head past the closed closet. Go through the pantry and into the kitchen. Walk past the kitchen up to the table in the dining room.

Turn left just past the stairs. Stop in the left doorway at the end of the hall.Walk down the hall in the direction of the stairs to the second floor. Pass the stairs and enter the living room. Take a right in the living room. Stop on the right of the chair at the head of the table.
Exit bedroom and walk down stairs. Stop at base of stairs.Walk up the stairs all the way to the top. Walk through the second doorway on your left, and stop immediatly once you walked through.
Go down the step turn left, walk down the flight of stairs, stop beside the refrigerator.Turn right and walk up the first set of stairs. Wait at the bottom of the second set of stairs.

Exit the room then head toward the black furniture straight ahead. When you get to it turn right and head all the way down passing the kitchen. Stop after you pass the kitchen.Walk straight into the hallway. Turn right and go into the room. Wait near the door on the left.
Go straight into the hall. Turn right and walk straight until you go into another room. Wait there.Turn completely around. Walk straight ahead through the doorway that is next to the giant urn.

Exit the room and walk straight ahead down the hallway. Stop in the area between the living room and dining room.Go straight into the third arch from the left. Turn right and go down the hallway until you get to stairs on the right. Go up two steps then stop.

Turn right and enter through the sliding door. Continue past the TV on the right. Enter the kitchen and wait beside the fridge.Walk up the small flight of stairs down the hall passed passing the refrigerator.

Walk to the right of the stairs. Continue past and to the right of the stairs that go down. Turn right and stop in the doorway of the double glass doors.Walk forward down the hall and turn right at the stairs. Walk past the stairs and into the next room. Wait near the entrance way.

Enter the room. Turn slightly right and walk straight to enter the other room using the door on the far right. Wait at the entrance.Walk through the dining room into the area with the tiled floor and exit sign.

Leave the room through an entryway next to the painting of a man with a white wig and go down the hall with a long row of paintings, and wait at the entry to another room on the other end.Walk through the dining room into the area with the tiled floor and exit sign.

Turn around, turn left at closet door. Take another left at bedroom door. Stop inside the second bedroom doorway.Walk through the door on the right side of the bed. Go straight through the closet and into the bathroom. Stop in front of the toilet.

With the door leading outside behind you, walk forward and turn left to go down the corridor with the eye chart towards your right. Continue past the half bath on your left and the kitchen on your right, then turn left. Enter the bedroom ahead of your though the leftmost door on the opposite wall.Exit the bedroom and take the first right. Stop just past the eye exam chart on the wall.

Go up stairs and turn left to stairs. Stop between stairs and large double doors.Go straight and turn right in front of the towards the 3 wicker decorations. Go straight down the hallway, enter the doorway, and wait.

Walk forward around the bed and out of the door on the left and into the office. In the office walk straight and take a right at the first hallway. In the hallway take a right into the hallway/entryway, and stop right next to the table on the right.Keeping the hanging wall mirror on your right, proceed onward up the hall until you reach another hallway on your left, go down that left hallway. You will know you are on the correct path if you see a framed photo of letters on the right wall. Continue moving forward until you pass the room on the left with the sink. Pivot to your right and travel in a forward direction down across the tile and then take a step onto the carpet in front of you. Stand on that carpet and wait for further instructions.

Turn around, go past the fridge, and then turn right and go up the steps. Just when you get to the top of the steps, stop. Wait there.Turn left, and walk down the stairs. Keep walking forward towards the dining table, and stop there.

Turn right passed the stairs and pass the couch. Enter the dining room. Continue down the hall and stop in the kitchen.Walk and turn left around the counter and walk straight towards the living room. Stop next to the couch entrance.

Exit the bathroom. Turn left. Then go into the bedroom nearest to the world map on the wall above a desk. Stop a couple of feet into the room.walk straight to hallway on right. turn right and follow hallway, at the end of hallway turn slight left and enter living room. Stop at couch.

Walk to the right of the stairs. Continue past and to the right of the stairs that go down. Turn right and stop in the doorway of the double glass doors.Exit the craft room and make a left. Go past the stairs that go downstairs and head towards the front door. Enter the formal living room and then pass into the dining room. Stop just before reaching the table and wait.

Walk out of the closet and take a right out of the room. Take a left and walk towards the living room. Stop nest to the rug in front of the couch next to the patio door.Go past the couch towards the kitchen area. Go between the kitchen and dining room table through the door way in the center. Turn right into the bedroom. Stop in front of the closet.

Enter the kitchen and walk past the refrigerator, then turn right. Proceed through the entryway and wait by the freezers.Walk straight and then turn right to exit the room. Turn left and go down the hallway. Turn left when you get to large glass doors on the right and wait near the clear vase with the white flowers.

Turn right and exit the bathroom. Walk down the hallway once you pass the wine cellar, keep to the right to enter the next hallway. Go to the end of that hallway and turn to stop on the bottom step of the stairs.Go around the stairs into the hallway. Walk down the hallway until you reach the end, take a right, and stop at the entrance to the living room.

With the foot of the bed behind you, exit the bedroom through the door on the left and walk to the top of the stairs. Go through the open door at the top of the stairs and enter the bedroom. Stop after entering this bedroom.Enter the open door opposite the stairs to go down. Make a right just before the round bedside table. Walk through the closet. Wait at the toilet.

walk towards the pool table, exit the room through the interior double doors, walk straight through the sitting area, walk into the arch way and stop inside of it.Walk straight through the doorway, take a sharp right through the next doorway and then walk straight until you've reached the bedroom, then stop.

With the door leading outside behind you, walk forward and turn left to go down the corridor with the eye chart towards your right. Continue past the half bath on your left and the kitchen on your right, then turn left. Enter the bedroom ahead of your though the leftmost door on the opposite wall.Head past the closed closet. Go through the pantry and into the kitchen. Walk past the kitchen up to the table in the dining room.

With the rope barrier directly to your right, move forward while staying on the carpet pathway and turn left when you reach the corner. Continue on the pathway until you reach a T intersection on the pathway and turn right to exit the room though a set of double doors.Go down the hallway opposite the roped off circle in the floor through the brown double doors, take a few steps into the dining room and stop.

Walk to the other side of the patio and enter the building through the sliding glass doors turn right and wait in the dining area.Walk through the door to the living room. Turn left and walk out the glass doors. Walk down the step. Stop on the lawn.
Enter the building and walk through the kitchen. Stop in the hall next to the ovens.Go forward and wait in tront of the sink.

Facing the toilet, walk through the door on the left. Make a right and walk through the doorway across the room. Make a left and walk down the hallway. Turn right at the next opening and stop before the kitchen island on the right.Turn right, walk straight through the arched door way, continue straight stop beside the bed.
Turn left. Walk towards clock. Turn right. Walk past kitchen. Stop one tile length past the end of the black couch.Walk past the kitchen and wait in the short hallway at the far end of the kitchen.
